{"tid":398902,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女朋友話唔去觀塘西太后開倉就分手","createTime":"2017-09-13T13:54:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T04:06:16.000Z","uid":69088,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e48a897f199fc3cb08dc891305f693b1622346ba","tid":398902,"uid":69088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T13:54:17.000Z","msg":"女朋友睇埋曬D垃撚垃《新xx》、《新xxxxxx》<br />\n話開倉銀包好撚抵屌，原來賣假貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好在堅持唔去，佢買唔撚到發左我一日脾氣<br />\n依家間野仲賣緊lego，爸打真係小心D<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n海關兩日前接獲投訴，指有散貨場於社交平台宣傳平價銀包，實則出賣冒牌貨。海關經深入調查，今日掩至觀塘開源道駱駝漆大廈一店舖，拘捕兩名男子(分別30及35歲)，其中一人係負責人，另一人則為售貨員，涉嫌違反《商品說明條例》。行動中，海關撿獲800個銀包，總值約36萬元，其售價比正貨平約一半。經商標持有人Vivienne Westwood核實，該散貨場以真貨及冒牌貨混合出售。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170913&amp;guid=57205832&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170913%26guid%3D57205832%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=E9yJEMmn1VVTMm8ooIaxq0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=c6d56787\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170913%26guid%3D57205832%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=a7e48537\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170913&amp;guid=57205832&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dc605e9571b6fa580a8a0dc87c38915d7ad55ff","tid":398902,"uid":69088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:02:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c951e7c0beed91cdddf859295c9505504c12f59","tid":398902,"uid":69088,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:13:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4